      • appendLiteralToken

        public final void appendLiteralToken(ASToken token)
        Append XML literal token to the contents of this node. If the last literal node of the contents is an XML literal (but not <>), the token is appended to the last literal node. Otherwise, a new LiteralNode is added.
        Parameters:
        token - XML literal token.
